      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i have this crazy headache right now. like it's the worst one i've ever had, just hit me out of nowhere. and i noticed my left eye looks a bit different, like the lid is drooping a little. do u think it could just be a huge migraine? i eat a lot of cheese and stuff so maybe it's an aura or something?",
